        <abstract> 
<p>Sends a single specimen of <hi rend="italic">Drosophyllum lusitanicum</hi> with description from F. de Avellar Brotero’s <hi rend="italic">Flora Lusitanica</hi> [1804].</p> 
            <p>Discusses Portuguese ferns,</p>
            <p>inherited mutilation,</p>
            <p>and the earth’s geological history.</p>
            <p>Evolution of behaviour and beauty by natural selection.</p>
        </abstract>
